articles.title: What Iowa caucus results say about GOP voters
articles.description: Iowa is only the first state in a monthslong nomination process for both parties. But is that process still achieving the results Americans desire? Lynn Vavreck, professor of American politics at UCLA, joins CBS News to discuss.
